summary: TONY STARK, IRON MAN VOL. 2 – STARK REALITIES TPB Written by DAN SLOTT & JEREMY WHITLEY Penciled by VALERIO SCHITI Cover by...
caption:
TONY STARK, IRON MAN VOL. 2 – STARK REALITIES TPB

Written by DAN SLOTT & JEREMY WHITLEY
Penciled by VALERIO SCHITI
Cover by ALEXANDER LOZANO
All-out war on multiple fronts! Arsenal, the monstrous robot that once took on all the Avengers, is back in an all-new way — just as Tony Stark changes everything with his virtual world known as the eScape! But who controls the eScape? Who controls the real world? And who controls Iron Man? The answer to at least one of these questions is the vile villain called the Controller. And the answer to the others might surprise you! Iron Man isn’t just a suit. It’s an idea, born of a genius. And in a place where thought and existence are one and the same, where Tony Stark’s imagination is unchecked, what kind of terrifying, all-powerful Iron Man will be born?! Reality, the cyberscape and Tony Stark’s heart, mind and soul at stake! Collecting TONY STARK, IRON MAN #6-11.
136 PGS./Rated T+ …$17.99
ISBN: 978-1-302-91273-4

summary: When Peter Parker gets fed up with Tumblr:
body:
When Peter Parker gets fed up with Tumblr:

Peter: Ugh, Tumblr is such garbage right now. I wish I could just, like, take over for a bit and fix all of these issues!

Tony: Yeah, I get that.

-One week later-

Media: Stark Industries to buy Tumblr?!

Peter: Mr. Stark, I didn’t mean for you to actually buy Tumblr!!

Tony: Well, it’s yours now. Try not to screw it up too much!

Peter: I guess it’s not like I could make it much worse…
